{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775871650286,"sessionID":"ses_285cdb4ddffem8xdXe9Ez0Bk8K","part":{"id":"prt_d7a32e9b9001KYnXiLillovxvD","messageID":"msg_d7a32de4300162DKa5PPVLICCw","sessionID":"ses_285cdb4ddffem8xdXe9Ez0Bk8K","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-3a1e914ac1294b4284091e9eb4b6f79a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-024/design.md","limit":150},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-024/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-024 — DockerService 封装 (DockerService Encapsulation)\n2: \n3: ## 模块信息\n4: \n5: - **模块**: `cmd/cli`\n6: - **语言**: Python\n7: - **规模**: M\n8: - **关联需求**: AR-024\n9: \n10: ## 架构概述\n11: \n12: ### 设计目标\n13: \n14: DockerService 是一个封装了 Docker SDK 操作的服务类，为 AgentCube CLI 的构建和发布工作流提供统一的 Docker 接口。该服务封装了 Docker SDK 的复杂性，提供了简洁的高级 API 用于镜像构建、推送、标记和管理等操作，同时提供完善的错误处理、日志记录和输入验证机制。\n15: \n16: ### 核心组件\n17: \n18: ```\n19: agentcube/services/\n20: ├── docker_service.py         # DockerService 主要实现\n21: ├── __init__.py               # 服务包导出\n22: └── [exceptions.py]           # 自定义异常类（可选）\n23: ```\n24: \n25: ### 架构原则\n26: \n27: 1. **封装复杂性**: 将 Docker SDK 的复杂性封装在服务层，提供简洁的高级 API\n28: 2. **延迟初始化**: Docker 客户端采用延迟初始化（Lazy Initialization）模式\n29: 3. **错误隔离**: 将 Docker SDK 异常包装为服务特定异常，避免直接暴露底层实现\n30: 4. **安全第一**: 妥善处理敏感信息（如密码），不记录到日志中\n31: 5. **可观测性**: 提供可选的详细日志模式，支持调试和故障排查\n32: 6. **幂等性**: 所有操作设计为幂等的，可以安全地重复执行\n33: \n34: ## 组件设计\n35: \n36: ### DockerService 类\n37: \n38: #### 数据结构\n39: \n40: ```python\n41: import logging\n42: import time\n43: from pathlib import Path\n44: from typing import Any, Dict, Optional\n45: \n46: import docker\n47: from docker.errors import DockerException\n48: \n49: \n50: logger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n51: \n52: \n53: class DockerService:\n54:     \"\"\"Service for Docker operations.\"\"\"\n55: \n56:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None:\n57:         \"\"\"Initialize the Docker service.\n58: \n59:         Args:\n60:             verbose: Enable verbose logging for debugging.\n61: \n62:         Raises:\n63:             RuntimeError: If Docker client initialization fails.\n64:         \"\"\"\n65:         self.verbose = verbose\n66:         if verbose:\n67:             logging.basicConfig(level=logging.DEBUG)\n68:         self._client: Optional[docker.DockerClient] = None\n69: \n70:     @property\n71:     def client(self) -> docker.DockerClient:\n72:         \"\"\"Get or create Docker client using lazy initialization.\n73: \n74:         Returns:\n75:             The Docker client instance.\n76: \n77:         Raises:\n78:             DockerException: If Docker daemon is not available.\n79:         \"\"\"\n80:         if self._client is None:\n81:             self._client = docker.from_env()\n82:         return self._client\n83: ```\n84: \n85: #### 公共 API 方法\n86: \n87: ##### 1. Docker 可用性检查\n88: \n89: ```python\n90: def check_docker_available(self) -> bool:\n91:     \"\"\"Check if Docker daemon is available and running.\n92: \n93:     Returns:\n94:         True if Docker is available, False otherwise.\n95: \n96:     Note:\n97:         This method does not raise exceptions on failure, making it\n98:         suitable for availability checks before operations.\n99:     \"\"\"\n100:     try:\n101:         self.client.ping()\n102:         return True\n103:     except DockerException as e:\n104:         logger.warning(f\"Docker not available: {e}\")\n105:         return False\n106: ```\n107: \n108: ##### 2. 镜像构建\n109: \n110: ```python\n111: def build_image(\n112:     self,\n113:     dockerfile_path: Path,\n114:     context_path: Path,\n115:     image_name: str,\n116:     tag: str = \"latest\",\n117:     build_args: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n118: ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n119:     \"\"\"Build a Docker image from a Dockerfile.\n120: \n121:     Args:\n122:         dockerfile_path: Path to the Dockerfile.\n123:         context_path: Path to the build context directory.\n124:         image_name: Name for the resulting image.\n125:         tag: Tag for the image (default: \"latest\").\n126:         build_args: Optional build arguments for proxy configuration.\n127: \n128:     Returns:\n129:         Dict containing:\n130:             - image_name: Full image name with tag.\n131:             - image_id: SHA256 hash of the image.\n132:             - image_size: Human-readable size string.\n133:             - size_bytes: Size in bytes.\n134:             - build_time: Timestamp of the build.\n135: \n136:     Raises:\n137:         FileNotFoundError: If dockerfile_path or context_path does not exist.\n138:         ValueError: If image_name or dockerfile_path is invalid.\n139:         RuntimeError: If Docker is not available or build fails.\n140:     \"\"\"\n141:     if not self.check_docker_available():\n142:         raise RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")\n143: \n144:     logger.info(f\"Building image {image_name}:{tag} from {dockerfile_path}\")\n145:     full_image_name = f\"{image_name}:{tag}\"\n146: \n147:     try:\n148:         image, build_logs = self.client.images.build(\n149:             path=str(context_path),\n150:             dockerfile=str(dockerfile_path),\n\n(Showing lines 1-150 of 1246. Use offset=151 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-024 — DockerService 封装 (DockerService Encapsulation)\n\n## 模块信息\n\n- **模块**: `cmd/cli`\n- **语言**: Python\n- **规模**: M\n- **关联需求**: AR-024\n\n## 架构概述\n\n### 设计目标\n\nDockerService 是一个封装了 Docker SDK 操作的服务类，为 AgentCube CLI 的构建和发布工作流提供统一的 Docker 接口。该服务封装了 Docker SDK 的复杂性，提供了简洁的高级 API 用于镜像构建、推送、标记和管理等操作，同时提供完善的错误处理、日志记录和输入验证机制。\n\n### 核心组件\n\n```\nagentcube/services/\n├── docker_service.py         # DockerService 主要实现","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-024/design.md","time":{"start":1775871650264,"end":1775871650284}}}}
